<item>
            <title>[OWB-434] ThreadLocal&lt;SingletonContext&gt; doen&apos;t get cleaned up</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OWB-434</link>
                <project id="12310844" key="OWB">OpenWebBeans</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We currently store the active SingletonContext for each thread in a ThreadLocal.&lt;br/&gt;
We must cleanup this ThreadLocal at the end of each request!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12471085">OWB-434</key>
            <summary>ThreadLocal&lt;SingletonContext&gt; doen&apos;t get cleaned up</summary>
